HEADWORD: Cowardize
<hw>Cow"ard*ize</hw> <pr>(-<?/z)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To render
cowardly</def>. <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>God . . . <qex>cowardizeth</qex> . . . insolent spirits.</q>
<rj><qau>Bp. Hall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cowardliness</ent>⟦br⟧
